data.description: Welcome to your updated 5-bedroom Cape Cod home in Maple Heights! Move-in ready, this residence features a first-floor bedroom for convenience. Modern upgrades seamlessly blend with classic charm, offering a stylish and comfortable living space. The chef's kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances. Enjoy the cozy fireplace in the living room and entertain in the formal dining room. Upstairs, find a tranquil master suite and additional bedrooms. The backyard is perfect for outdoor gatherings. Conveniently located near schools, parks, and amenities, this home invites you to embrace the Maple Heights lifestyle. Don't miss out – schedule your showing today!
